waittime <- cfs.df %>% 
    filter(discretionary == FALSE & 
               RPD_Anscombe_Trans == 1) %>%
    group_by(CallTypeCode, RPD_Priority) %>% 
    summarise(MedianWaitTime = median(RPD_Response_Time),
              Count = n()) %>%
    arrange(desc(Count)) %>%
    mutate(Prop = Count / sum(Count)) %>%
    filter(Prop > .01)
